"""
Builds a simple application which tests LCD rendering code.

This will build the example:
    $ scons

This will start the LCD renderer (requires wxPython)
    $ mkfifo lcd_fifo
    $ ./lcd_render.py &
    $ ./lcd_test

Copyright (c) 2012-2013 theJPster (github@thejpster.org.uk)

